    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BULLETHEART</strong> is a fast-paced, adrenaline-pumping, first-person movement shooter where your ammo is limited to the number of enemies in the current level, so you must use smooth movement and precise aim to progress. But be careful, you can only take one shot before dying. Complete the level by learning its layout and by planning with subsequent attempts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326770/extras/8c13b49b0baa65d551ad9de7e1a771ae.poster.avif?t=1766051815\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326770/extras/8c13b49b0baa65d551ad9de7e1a771ae.webm?t=1766051815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326770/extras/8c13b49b0baa65d551ad9de7e1a771ae.mp4?t=1766051815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhance yourself with randomized upgrades using bullets as currency before you begin, max out your overdrive meter quickly enough to unlock a destructive skill to use against enemies, and take advantage of basic movement mechanics like dashing, sliding, and double-jumping complimented by more flashy combat mechanics. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326770/extras/86f8a0c8c0705586d95ca20b6065698e.poster.avif?t=1766051815\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326770/extras/86f8a0c8c0705586d95ca20b6065698e.webm?t=1766051815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326770/extras/86f8a0c8c0705586d95ca20b6065698e.mp4?t=1766051815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
